extendedInfo.description: IVF-Worldwide.com is the largest and most comprehensive in-vitro fertilization (IVF)-focused website for doctors, embryologists, nurses and social workers. It links specialists to encourage dialogue, discuss special treatments and medications, and advance research. The website aims to have   the largest and most comprehensive online marketplace in the field of IVF.IVF-Worldwide.com was founded by Professor Zeev Shoham and Professor Milton Leong, two medically-renowned doctors, both experts and pioneers in the field of reproductive endocrinology and infertility.

reviews.title: Not an app
